Delphi Juicer
A rare Juicer variant whose harness includes psionic enhancers, granting
limited clairvoyance alongside standard physical enhancements. Delphi Juicers
are prized as scouts and forward observers: their ability to sense evil and
detect magic makes them invaluable to any team.

Like all Juicers, Delphi models gain massive physical bonuses from their drug
harness and face a shortened lifespan. Unlike standard Juicers, they also gain
ISP (psionic energy) and can use Sense Evil and Sense Magic as psionic-adjacent
abilities. Skill picks come from Physical, Espionage, Pilot, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9, ME 10.
ISP: Starting ISP pool grows each level.
Starting equipment: Delphi Juicer harness (fitted), medium body armor,
two weapons, and one year drug supply.
